HEADWORD: Onomatopoetic
<hw>On`o*mat`o*po*et"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to onomatopoeia; characterized by onomatopoeia; imitative;
<as>as, an <ex>onomatopoetic</ex> writer or word</as>.</def>
